These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, skiing, parkour, skateboarding
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, 7up, coffee, hot-chocolate
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, blend, montecristo, game
1. the bolivar-smoker is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
2. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an odd position##4
4. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the game-smoker##3
5. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
6. the game-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
7. the blend-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
8. the game-smoker is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Sport         | skateboarding      | ice-hockey | skiing | parkour |
| Beverage   | coffee | soy-milk  | 7up   | hot-chocolate    |
| Cigar     | bolivar     | montecristo    | game    | blend      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, ebony, red, brown
4 different pets are kept: turtle, snake, pony, chinchilla
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, metal, electronic, gospel
1. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the person who likes red##3
2. the person who likes brown is the owner of the pony##1
3. the person who likes red is in an even position##4
4. the fan of classical is on the far right##1
5. the fan of gospel is on the far left##1
6. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
7. the owner of the turtle is between the person who likes brown and the person who likes ebony##2
8. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the snake and the person who likes red##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Color         | brown | red   | ebony | mauve  |
| Pet   | pony     | turtle | chinchilla  | snake |
| Music-Genre     | gospel        | electronic  | metal    | classical |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
4 different pets are kept: mouse, chinchilla, rat, frog
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, badminton, biathlon, skiing
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, soul, reggae, rock
1. the person who's sport is skiing is between the owner of the mouse and the owner of the frog##2
2. the person who's sport is badminton is the fan of rock##1
3. the fan of techno is the owner of the rat##1
4. the fan of techno is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
5. the owner of the frog is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the owner of the chinchilla and the person who's sport is golf##2
7. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Pet          | mouse | chinchilla   | frog     | rat     |
| Sport   | badminton  | skiing | biathlon   | golf  |
| Music-Genre     | rock      | soul | reggae | techno |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, motorbike, quad-bike, boat
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, purple, amber, azure
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, blend, siglo, dannemann
1. the person who likes azure is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the motorbike is the blend-smoker##1
3. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the game-smoker##1
4. the person who likes purple is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
5. the person who likes azure is the game-smoker##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is the person who likes aquamarine##1
7. the person who likes amber is the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Transport   | bike  | boat   | quad-bike     | motorbike |
| Color   | amber  | azure      | aquamarine        | purple     |
| Cigar         | siglo | game | dannemann | blend   |

