.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, traveling, puzzles, cooking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, trance, metal, dubstep
City: venice, miami, edinburgh, paris
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is the fan of dubstep##1
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an odd position##4
3. the person traveling to venice is the fan of dubstep##1
4. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
5. the person traveling to venice is in an even position##4
6. the fan of trance is on the far left##1
7. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left or right of the person traveling to edinburgh##3
9. the fan of country is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Hobby   | gardening   | cooking   | puzzles | traveling |
| Music-Genre         | trance      | dubstep | country      | metal |
| City     | miami | venice        | paris       | edinburgh  |

