.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, september, june, march
4 different games are played: chess, whist, backgammon, domino
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, water, mirinda, tea
1. the person who's birthday is in september is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
3. the person drinking cola is the person who's birthday is in september##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person drinking water##1
5. the person playing whist is on the far right##1
6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
7. the person who's birthday is in march is in an even position##4
8. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Birthday    | june   | march      | september       | july |
| Game   | chess | domino | backgammon     | whist |
| Beverage     | tea     | water  | cola | mirinda |

