.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, dressmaker, security-guard, musician
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, train, trike, subway
House: victorian, cape-cod, palace, art-deco
1. the palace house is the person driving the ship##1
2. the cape-cod house is between the person driving the subway and the victorian house##2
3. the person driving the subway is the dressmaker##1
4. the person driving the train is on the left or right of the dressmaker##3
5. the pilot is in an even position##4
6. the person driving the subway is on the right of the musician##1
7. the person driving the ship is the pilot##1
8. the palace house is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Job      | security-guard   | musician          | dressmaker | pilot        |
| Transport   | trike     | train | subway   | ship     |
| House           | victorian | cape-cod         | art-deco         | palace |

