.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, snooker, bridge, whist
4 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, frog, snake
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, coffee, hot-chocolate, fanta
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
2. the owner of the frog is the person playing mah-jongg##1
3. the owner of the snake is the person playing bridge##1
4. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
5. the person drinking coffee is between the owner of the cat and the person playing mah-jongg##2
6. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
7. the person playing mah-jongg is in an even position##4
8. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person playing snooker and the person playing bridge##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Game         | snooker | mah-jongg      | bridge       | whist    |
| Pet           | ferret  | frog  | snake | cat |
| Beverage   | fanta      | hot-chocolate | coffee         | iced-tea    |

