.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, bellflower, daffodil, orchid
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, vegafina, aristoff, bolivar
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, gospel, indie, house
1. the dunhill-smoker is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growsbegonia is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker##3
3. the person who growsorchid is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker##3
4. the fan of gospel is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
5. the person who growsbellflower is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
6. the fan of house is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
7. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
8. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
9. the bolivar-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Flower   | bellflower         | begonia  | daffodil     | orchid         |
| Cigar        | bolivar | vegafina | dunhill | aristoff         |
| Music-Genre      | gospel         | indie  | funk   | house |

