.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
City: miami, venice, nizza, marseilles
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, iced-tea, milk
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, davidoff, aristoff, dannemann
 1. the aristoff-smoker is on the left or right of the person traveling to nizza##3
 2. the person drinking juice is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
 4. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person traveling to venice and the person traveling to miami##2
 5. the dannemann-smoker is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3
 6. the dannemann-smoker is the person traveling to nizza##1
 7. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1
 8. the person traveling to miami is in an odd position##4
 9. the person drinking lemonade is between the person traveling to marseilles and the person traveling to nizza##2
10. the aristoff-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| City   | miami  | nizza    | venice | marseilles    |
| Beverage   | juice | iced-tea | lemonade  | milk |
| Cigar           | aristoff   | dannemann    | oliveros        | davidoff   |

