.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, ship, train, scooter
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, february, september, december
House: victorian, cape-cod, wooden, colonial
1. the person driving the boat is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
3. the colonial house is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
4. the person who's birthday is in february is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the train is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
6. the colonial house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
7. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
8. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the cape-cod house##3
9. the person driving the boat is on the left of the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Transport      | boat                | scooter  | ship | train   |
| Birthday           | december | february | november   | september |
| House   | cape-cod         | victorian     | colonial     | wooden |

