.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, indonesian, spanish, italian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, badminton, biathlon, cycling
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, blue, pink, turquise
1. the indonesian is on the left of the italian##1
2. the spanish is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes blue is on the left or right of the person who likes turquise##3
4. the spanish is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
5. the person who likes amber is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who likes turquise##2
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an even position##4
7. the canadian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Nationality          | spanish    | indonesian  | italian  | canadian |
| Sport   | cycling | badminton | golf | biathlon |
| Color   | pink    | amber     | turquise    | blue |

