City: san-francisco, venice, colone, hamburg
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, bongani, chaman, fonseca
1. the bongani-smoker is between the person who likes coral and the person traveling to san-francisco##2
2. the person who likes purple is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person traveling to colone is on the left or right of the chaman-smoker##3
4. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
5. the fonseca-smoker is in an odd position##4
6. the person who likes light-blue is on the left or right of the chaman-smoker##3
7. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg##3
8. the person traveling to colone is the person who likes purple##1
9. the person traveling to hamburg is between the chaman-smoker and the dannemann-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Color      | purple | coral      | light-blue  | lavender    |
| City   | colone   | venice | hamburg | san-francisco |
| Cigar           | fonseca      | chaman       | bongani   | dannemann      |

