.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, chaman, bluemaster, aristoff
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, green, coral, blue
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, western, action, disaster
1. the bluemaster-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the chaman-smoker is between the aristoff-smoker and the person watching mystery movies##2
3. the person watching western movies is on the far left or far right##3
4. the aristoff-smoker is in an even position##4
5. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
6. the person who likes blue is between the person watching mystery movies and the person who likes apricot##2
7. the person watching western movies is on the far right##1
8. the person who likes green is in an even position##4
9. the person watching mystery movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Cigar         | dannemann    | bluemaster | chaman  | aristoff  |
| Color   | coral | green       | blue | apricot |
| Movie-Genre         | action   | mystery      | disaster | western       |

