.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-15::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, august, march, october
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, bellflower, balloon-flower, zinnia
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, designer, doctor, journalist
1. the designer is in an even position##4
2. the designer is the person who's birthday is in august##1
3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is the person who growszinnia##1
5. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left##1
6. the person who growsamaryllis is the designer##1
7. the freelancer is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
8. the journalist is the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| Birthday      | march      | august | july     | october    |
| Flower   | zinnia | amaryllis      | bellflower | balloon-flower |
| Job           | doctor   | designer  | freelancer     | journalist |

