1. the person who likes black is on the left or right of the person who likes amber##3
2. the gothic-revival house is in an even position##4
3. the owner of the rat is on the far left##1
4. the tower house is on the left or right of the person who likes light-blue##3
5. the person who likes amber is between the owner of the pony and the farmhouse house##2
6. the owner of the hedgehog is the futuristic house##1
7. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person who likes black##1
8. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person who likes black##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Color    | yellow    | amber     | black    | light-blue        |
| House       | farmhouse   | gothic-revival | tower | futuristic |
| Pet   | rat | guinea-pig      | pony    | hedgehog   |

