.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
City: marseilles, rome, colone, berlin
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, apricot, green, orange
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, december, august, may
1. the person traveling to marseilles is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes orange is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person who likes black##3
4. the person traveling to colone is on the far left##1
5. the person traveling to rome is between the person who likes orange and the person who likes black##2
6. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who likes black##1
7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
8. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| City    | colone    | rome    | marseilles  | berlin |
| Color   | orange | apricot | black | green      |
| Birthday     | december   | june        | may   | august       |

 